# Commons-fetched thumbnail presets: keep the image lean by excluding the full-res
# originals/ and every fetched preset. Fetch them post-deploy:
# manage.py fetch_commons_thumbnail --from-file
# Kept: the hand-made SVGs (tiny) and The School of Athens, which the login banner uses.
static/homework/img/thumbnails/*
!static/homework/img/thumbnails/README.md
!static/homework/img/thumbnails/sources.txt
!static/homework/img/thumbnails/template.json
!static/homework/img/thumbnails/aurora.*
!static/homework/img/thumbnails/ember.*
!static/homework/img/thumbnails/meadow.*
!static/homework/img/thumbnails/the-school-of-athens-by-raffaello-sanzio-da-urbino.*
